	<body>
            <img src="../shared/images/bg1_normal.png" style="height:0px; width:0px; float:left; opacity: 0">
            <img src="../shared/images/bg2_normal.png" style="height:0px; width:0px; float:left; opacity: 0">
            <div id="content"> 
                    <div id="pageTitle">Planning the Appropriate Environment</div>
                    <div id="instruction_text">Take a look at the two pictures of an office space. Imagine yourself interviewing a candidate. Which one would you prefer? Click the image to learn more.</div>
                    <div id="messy_desk" class="active" rel="1" audio_name="module2_messy">
                        
                    </div>
                    <div id="tidy_desk" class="active" rel="2" audio_name="module2_tidy">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div id="content_text">
                        <div id="btn_close" style=" position: absolute; margin-left: 300px; z-index: 99999; cursor: pointer;"><img src="../shared/images/close_button.png"></div>
                        <div class="header_text"><span style="color:#cc0000">Messy Desk</span> </div>
                            <p>A messy or a cluttered desk is a sign of a cluttered mind. Can you find what you need from the clutter without wasting time? Not really! </p>
                            <p>Imagine the first impression it can have on candidates. Remember that you are representing Test My Interview and are its face.</p>
                            <p>Ensure that your interview area is organized and all the cables are neatly tucked away from view.</p>
                            <center>
                                <div style=" margin-top: -10px;"><img src="../shared/images/td.png"></div>
                            </center>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div id="content_text1">
                        <div id="btn_close1" style=" position: absolute; margin-left: 300px; z-index: 99999; cursor: pointer;"><img src="../shared/images/close_button.png"></div>  
                        <div class="header_text" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #1eac17;"> <span style="color:#1eac17">Tidy Desk</span></div>
                            <p>A tidy desk is a sign of professionalism. </p>
                            <p id="text1">People often judge your capabilities based on the state of your desk. A clean, clutter–free desk creates a very positive impression about the organization you represent – Test My Interview!</p>
                            <center>
                                <div style=" margin-top:100px; margin-left: 30px;"> <img src="../shared/images/tu.png"></div>
                            </center>
                    </div>
                    <div id="active1" style="position: absolute; top:159px; width: 810px; border: 0px solid; height: 344px; left:102px;"> </div>
            </div>
	</body>
            <script type="text/javascript">
                var anim_flag = false; var total_steps = 2; var steps = Array(); var steps_handle = Array(); parent.next_disable();
                for(i=1;i<=total_steps;i++) steps[i] = Array();
                steps[1][0] = 'playStep1()'; steps[1][1] = 60000; steps[1][2] = 0;
                steps[2][0] = 'playStep2()'; steps[2][1] = 8200; steps[2][2] = 0;
                $(window).load(function() {
                parent.loadAudioTranscript('module2_l4','',true,false);
                });

                function postAudioPlay(){
                    anim_flag = true;
                    for(i=1;i<=total_steps;i++) {
                        steps_handle[i] = setTimeout(steps[i][0],steps[i][1]);
                    }
                    
			if($('#content').css('visibility')=='hidden') {
                                $('#content').css('display','none');
				$('#content').css('visibility','visible').fadeIn('normal');
			}
                }

                function pauseAnimation(current_time) {  
                    anim_flag = false;
                    for(i=1;i<=steps_handle.length;i++) {
                        if(steps[i][2]==0) clearTimeout(steps_handle[i]);
                    }
                }
                function resumeAnimation(current_time) {
                    anim_flag = true;
                    if(current_time>0) {
                        current_time = Math.floor(parseInt(current_time)) * 1000;
                        ii = 1;
                        for(j=1;j<=total_steps;j++) {
                            if(current_time<= steps[j][1]) ii = j; break;
                        }

                        for(k=ii;k<=total_steps;k++) { steps_handle[k] = setTimeout(steps[k][0],steps[k][1] - current_time); }
                    }
                }
                
                function playStep1() { 
                    if(anim_flag==true) { 
                        $('#messy_desk').fadeIn('normal',function() { steps[1][2] = 1; });
                        
                    }
                }
		function playStep2() { 
                    if(anim_flag==true) { 
                        $('#active1').fadeOut('normal', function() { steps[2][2] = 1; });
                    }
                }
		
                $(document).ready(function(){ 
                    var cont=0; var cont1=0;
                    $('.active').click(function(){
                        //$('.active').removeClass('selected');
                        $(this).addClass('selected');
                        var audio_file = $(this).attr('audio_name');
                        //parent.loadAudioTranscript(audio_file,'',true);
                        var number = $(this).attr('rel');
                        if(number == 1){ $(this).addClass('visited');  $('#content_text').fadeIn('fast'); } else if(number == 2 ){ cont1++; $('#content_text1').fadeIn('fast'); $(this).addClass('visited'); }
                        
                        if($('#messy_desk').hasClass('visited') && $('#tidy_desk').hasClass('visited') ){
                            parent.loadAudioTranscript(audio_file,'',true,true);
                        }
                        else{
                            parent.loadAudioTranscript(audio_file,'',true,false);
                        }
                    });
                    
                    $('#btn_close').click(function(){
                        $('#content_text').fadeOut();
                        $('#messy_desk').removeClass('selected');
			parent.unloadAudioTranscript();
                        
                    });
                   
                    $('#btn_close1').click(function(){
                        $('#content_text1').fadeOut();
                        $('#tidy_desk').removeClass('selected');
			parent.unloadAudioTranscript();
                    });
                   
                    
                });       
            </script>
</html>